 discuss the non-adiabatic excitations in the context of\nthe O2 spin transition during the dissociation process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2011 09:43:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2011 12:50:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2011 05:35:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
