e\nexplore its relationships with the other generalizations of the SN. We give\nsome results concerning the SNB distribution. In particular we derive the exact\ndistributions of the largest order statistic from SNB with parameters m and 1\nand the shortest order statistic SNB with parameters m and -1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2011 09:53:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
